{"tid":1442804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角要智取","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:30:11.000Z","uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"381b6963e16934525f03582129f05eadcaab1cd3","tid":1442804,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:12:00.000Z","msg":"出得嚟打人嘅北角佬有幾多係後生，係讀過書？但我哋唔同，好多大專大學生，又有專業人士。而且對IT同新科技都有良好認識。<br />\n<br />\n相反，硬碰我哋真係幾蝕。我哋打人係唔夠狠，唔可以攞棍攞刀，跟本冇同等武器。但我哋可以用航拍機監察住周圍，睇下佢邊度人多。航拍機亦都可以用嚟低飛，誘敵，引佢哋落單。"},{"pid":"1dee43663112f15e97692bc71e6d01a98f346eb8","tid":1442804,"uid":153476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"Be Water<br />\nBe Safe<br />\nSupport <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e449392968e733de77cb817c30ada28e53b58548","tid":1442804,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"071f3ca5388002f49d8e4b1c67fed948fd642ce1","tid":1442804,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"政府北角呢步棋 我地點行都反攻唔到<br />\n所以要好好防守 下一步將佢軍"}]}